* Data structures - struct

Struct's structure is constructed like this:

    type Place struct {
    	Name string
    	FunnyName bool
    }

To create an instance:

    Place{Name: "Brown Willy (UK)", FunnyName: false}

or:

    Place{"Ofakim (Israel)", true}

