* channels

Best (?) way to have goroutines talk to each other.

Creating a channel:

    mychannel1 := make(chan string)
    mychannel2 := make(chan string, 2)

Putting stuff into it:

    mychannel1 <- "going it"

Taking stuff out of it:

    message := <- mychannel1

